Following ston (staff on) StaffCode generates staff pieces and leger lines automatically, and any staff-piece code will change what kind of staff is generated. The default is st5ln (staff 5 lines).
StaffCode maps note names C1 D1 E1 .. C7 to staff positions based on the preceding clef and its staff position. If there has been no clef, treble staff positioning is used.
